'''Jacksonville''', Florida is a city in the United States. The city contains the neighbourhood of Grogans Bluff, which has street names that are mostly based on [[The Hobbit|''The Hobbit'']] and somewhat on ''[[The Lord of the Rings]].''<ref>{{Cite web|articleurl=https://www.thejaxsonmag.com/article/ten-jax-neighborhoods-with-thematic-street-names/#:~:text=Grogans%20Bluff%20and%20Lord%20of%20the%20Rings&text=A%20few%20names%20you%20find,King%20Lane%20and%20Wilderland%20Drive.|articlename=Ten Jax neighborhoods with thematic street names|author=Ten Jax neighborhoods with thematic street names|dated=30 March 2022|accessed=31 October 2024}}</ref>
